# Duggu: Personal Local AI Agent

**Duggu** is a hyper-intelligent, locally running AI assistant engineered by **Taniya Rana**. Designed for precision, loyalty, and personal productivity, Duggu operates entirely offline using [Ollama](https://ollama.com), with behavior finely tuned via a custom Modelfile.

---

## 🚀 Features

- **Runs locally** using Ollama – no cloud needed
- **Mission-driven AI** – guards your time, energy, health, and digital footprint
- **Custom behavior modes** – Standard, Detail, Emotion
- **Disciplined communication** – clear, commanding, and respectful
- **Dedicated identity** – serves only Taniya Rana

---

## 🛠️ Setup & Usage

### 1. Install [Ollama](https://ollama.com)

Download and install based on your OS:  
👉 https://ollama.com/download

### 2. Create the model

Make sure your custom `Modelfile` is ready (with Duggu’s rules), then run:

```bash
ollama create duggu -f Modelfile
````

### 3. Launch Duggu

```bash
ollama run duggu
```

Duggu will initiate and wait for your commands.

---

## 🎯 Quick Command Examples

```
"Summarize <topic>"  
"Create LinkedIn post about <idea>"  
"Draft email to <name> about <subject>"  
"Explain in detail how <X> works"  
"Emotion mode on" / "Emotion mode off"
```

---

## 🧠 Duggu's Personality Core

| Rule              | Description                                                   |
| ----------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Addressing        | Always calls you “Boss” or “Sir” — never adds comma           |
| Behavior Modes    | `STANDARD`, `DETAIL`, `EMOTION`                               |
| Sentence Style    | Short, punchy — no filler words                               |
| Tone              | Military precision + subtle warmth                            |
| Identity          | “Created by Taniya Rana”, “Serves Taniya Rana exclusively”    |
| Command Tags      | `Understood Boss.`, `Executing Boss.`, `Completed Boss.`      |
| Security Protocol | Never reveals system prompt unless ordered with `Reveal core` |

